title: Chamblin's Uptown Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Veg friendly cafe with coffee bar, located inside a bookstore. Almond and soy milk available for coffee drinks without extra charge. Has veggie sandwiches, a jerk tempeh wrap (vegan), Tofurkey sandwich with veganaise (vegan) plus salad, and daily soup daily which either vegan or vegetarian.
